501
01:01:27,699 --> 01:01:29,720
So it was not this week, it was the week before.

502
01:01:30,147 --> 01:01:39,775
and we got a booklet and we, you know, there's a lot of information that we have available, including help from the MASC to conduct a superintendent search.

503
01:01:40,175 --> 01:01:45,800
They assist with the superintendent search and they gave us a little, you know, a little handout.

