524
01:04:08,632 --> 01:04:15,096
We've also had the opportunity to talk, you know, they will do superintendent searches.

525
01:04:15,156 --> 01:04:21,739
There is a process with them that we could choose to, at the time, ask for their assistance.

526
01:04:22,100 --> 01:04:26,942
Of course, no decision like that has been made, but we are well aware of that as a potential.

527
01:04:27,182 --> 01:04:31,885
By the way, Angela, I did want to tell you that I did not receive an email from you, and that's been a problem.

528
01:04:31,925 --> 01:04:37,148
Somehow emails that are sent directly to the school are not coming to me, so use my Gmail address.

529
01:04:37,814 --> 01:04:38,074
please.

530
01:04:39,135 --> 01:04:51,460
So again, no way would I allow someone with 26 years of experience on the Medford School Committee, who lives and breathes this job, would I allow this to be a haphazard process.

531
01:04:52,781 --> 01:04:58,503
I also want to remind everybody that this year, we've had three new school committees join us.

