01:05:03,700 --> 01:05:04,941
They joined us in January.

537
01:05:05,602 --> 01:05:10,747
That was not the time to spring into action to do the superintendent's evaluation.

538
01:05:11,167 --> 01:05:20,356
They needed an opportunity to work with the superintendent and find out for themselves what kind of man he is.

539
01:05:21,419 --> 01:05:29,067
You don't just go and evaluate somebody who you've only worked for for six weeks.

540
01:05:29,748 --> 01:05:33,332
So our evaluation process is a little later this year, okay?

541
01:05:33,432 --> 01:05:34,593
It is going to happen.

