01:07:50,277 --> 01:07:51,518
We have a meeting on May 23rd.

566
01:07:51,558 --> 01:07:53,320
We have a meeting on May 24th.

567
01:07:53,340 --> 01:07:54,981
We have the M Club dinner on the 25th.

