01:07:55,481 --> 01:07:56,562
We have 6th, 7th, 8th.

569
01:07:57,243 --> 01:07:59,084
We are incredibly busy.

570
01:07:59,224 --> 01:08:01,346
It is, we have to get all of us together.

571
01:08:01,666 --> 01:08:02,967
Now, should this be a priority?

