01:08:20,245 --> 01:08:34,488
We will go through the extraordinary busy time of getting the budget, and we need to realize that the superintendent and his, everybody in the administration needs to spend time to put that budget together.

579
01:08:35,008 --> 01:08:36,668
That's the time of year it is.

580
01:08:36,688 --> 01:08:45,570
I assure you that this will not be a haphazard process, and I want to add, over my dead body.

