894
01:30:19,948 --> 01:30:21,288
The new mayor has a new start.

895
01:30:21,848 --> 01:30:24,349
She's got a long way to go, a long way to go.

896
01:30:25,111 --> 01:30:28,032
And it's not bad to review.

897
01:30:28,072 --> 01:30:28,973
Oh, and the overlap.

